e lodge and sequoia village inn llc filed a classaction lawsuit in california accusing the company and its partners of brazen deceit by coordinating with internet search engines and social media institutions to return false results on lodging entities in favor of those affiliated with their websites in violation of the lanham act the case is pending referencesedit  a b c d e f lead digital arbeiten bei trivago keine hierarchien und  biersorten gratis  grunderszene ranking  a b expedia inc expedia announces agreement to acquire majority of trivago  a b c d e f g h grunderszene trivago auf leisen sohlen  stellant partners howzat media invests in trivago the germanbased travel website focused on hotels reviews  community  grunderszene insight steigt zu millionenbewertung bei trivago ein  expedia to acquire stake in german hotel site reuters  retrieved    rp online mit  jahren den exit geschafft  anrej lehnert linkedin  a b c skift interview trivago building big team in shift toward directhotel relationships  a b c d e hospitality net trivago unveils plans for new global campus  skift trivago acquisition of hoteltech startup highlights evolution of booking sites  grunderszene mit altbier zu neuen startupvisionen  expedias hotel search service trivago plans ipo fortune retrieved    roof katie trivago closes up  in public debut techcrunch retrieved    trivago  expedia inc expedia inc retrieved    quora how much does trivago charge hotels per provision  hotel marketing trivago helps hotels manage online presence  hotel insight worried about how to optimse your hotel on ota websites trivago offer a helping hand  pulsoturistico trivago desembarca en argentina  a b mashable  apps to save you money  cnet trivago  the hotel search for android  usa today homeexchangecom wins best appwebsite for booking your stay  independent save time and money when booking your holiday with these handy apps  newscomau the  top apps to take on holiday  mercado continuo trivago inaugura oficinas 